Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A máscara...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.65,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A máscara do Dragão Azul...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.03,0:00:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.66,0:00:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Olhar nos olhos dele irá transformá-lo em pedra!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedra?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.24,0:00:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Ele veio para nos matar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.41,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O Dragão Azul me salvou.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele não mataria alguém sem razão.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ele fechou seus olhos.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Será que está dizendo para eles \N que não representa ameaça?
